    BlueprintsNeo4jOptionsBuilder, BlueprintsOptionsBuilder

    public abstract class AbstractBlueprintsOptionsBuilder<B extends AbstractBlueprintsOptionsBuilder<B,O>,O extends AbstractBlueprintsOptions>
extends AbstractPersistenceOptionsBuilder<B,O>
    An abstract PersistenceOptionsBuilder that provides utility methods to create generic Blueprints options.

    Created options can be BlueprintsResourceOptions if they define resource-level features, or BlueprintsStoreOptions if they define database access feature.

    All features are all optional: options can be created using all or none of them.

    See Also:
    BlueprintsResourceOptions, BlueprintsStoreOptions
